           </div> 
           <div class="slide-cap left"> 
            <h2>Construction of Phuket highway will kick off by 2023: Transport Ministry</h2> 
            <div class="p">
              The construction of the Muang Mai-Koh Kaew Highway should begin by 2023, Transport Minister Saksayam Chidchob said. 
